fields.Title: WHIRLING F3 / KLAASJE FULL STORY
fields.Description:
6) hardie confessed, whole story (ruby leader)
7) drama white (ruby suspect)

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "Shush. I can't hear what she's sayi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Shush. I can't hear what she's saying.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Why *did* you waste our time then?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why *did* you waste our time then?"

fields.Title: Volition: "C'mon. She lied through her teeth...."
fields.Dialogue Text: C'mon. She lied through her teeth. And you know it.

fields.Title: You: ""What's the RCM's involvement with..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What's the RCM's involvement with the Moralintern got to do with this?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "Until the lieutenant loses patience..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Until the lieutenant loses patience: "What does our *limited cooperation* with the MI have to do with this?"

fields.Title: You: ""Why did you call the cops if you'r..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why did you call the cops if you're hiding?"

fields.Title: You: ""Why didn't you run away from here?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why didn't you run away from here? As a matter of fact -- why are you here now?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""11.30 to 12.15. I don't know the e..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "11.30 to 12.15. I don't know the exact time. Around midnight."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""No..." She smiles nervously. The b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No..." She smiles nervously. The beads of her teeth shine.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""She said she'd take care of this...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She said she'd take care of this. It's what she does, you know. Take care of things. I helped her get the body to the bathroom -- we used a belt to pull him up under the shower. To keep him upright."

fields.Title: You: ""Just a hunch -- then what?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Just a hunch -- then what?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""About twenty, yes. Ruby explained..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "About twenty, yes. Ruby explained it would make the blood... you know what it does." She looks at the ground. Then raises her light brown eyes to meet yours.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She blinks, without averting her ga..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She blinks, without averting her gaze.

fields.Title: You: ""Why?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why?"

fields.Title: You: ""Okay. I'd like you to answer some..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay. I'd like you to answer some other questions, miss." (Conclude.)

fields.Title: Drama: "Stop staring and say something dram..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Stop staring and say something dramatic and professional!

fields.Title: You: ""Devil woman...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Devil woman..."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Okay, yes -- it's not." She's corn..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay, yes -- it's not." She's cornered. "It's not my name."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I didn't show up to a rendezvous...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I didn't show up to a rendezvous. They don't take that *lightly*." She rushes to explain: "I didn't show up because I was afraid they'd... do something to me. The job was finished -- I'm just a liability now."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She nods. "It was a sentimental thi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She nods. "It was a sentimental thing. I wanted to be more *me* here. This time. So I used my nickname."

fields.Title: You: ""Who gave it to you?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who gave it to you?"

fields.Title: You: "Say nothing. (Proceed.)"
fields.Dialogue Text: Say nothing. (Proceed.)

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "She's filling dead air. Can't stand..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She's filling dead air. Can't stand the silence.

fields.Title: You: "(Turn to the lieutenant.) "Kim, why..."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Turn to the lieutenant.) "Kim, why have we not *arrested* her yet?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Klaasje..." she repeats with a pai..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Klaasje..." she repeats with a pained smile on her face, her back pressed against the railing.

fields.Title: Drama: "See?!"
fields.Dialogue Text: See?!

fields.Title: Half Light: "Fucking *mind* games! Enough!"
fields.Dialogue Text: Fucking *mind* games! Enough!

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Good." He turns to her, the cuffs..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Good." He turns to her, the cuffs still in his hand. "What -- in your relationship -- made you think she's romantically interested in you?"

fields.Title: Volition: "It also has startlingly little to d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It also has startlingly little to do with arresting her, you suddenly realize...

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I know what this sounds like. That..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I know what this sounds like. That's why I didn't want to tell you before." She raises her eyes to meet yours. "But she *knew* what had happened -- when I came downstairs."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Did you hear or see the shooter in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Did you hear or see the shooter in the course of this?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""*Everything* could change." She lo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "*Everything* could change." She looks around. "This city, the extradition rules... The people after me could be in jail. Or maybe Revachol..." She falls silent.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I know, but..." She doesn't know w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I know, but..." She doesn't know what to say.

fields.Title: You: "It doesn't matter. Better not to me..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It doesn't matter. Better not to mention it.

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "Ruby?!"
fields.Dialogue Text: Ruby?!

fields.Title: Volition: "...or maybe you should take her to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: ...or maybe you should take her to the station? For safekeeping. She *lied* to you. And she's a flight risk.

fields.Title: Drama: "Who... what... Dear god, you've bee..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Who... what... Dear god, you've been lied to! She could have killed her lover and lied to everyone! She's not *candid* at all, she's smoke and mirrors and will-o-wisps!
fields.Alternate1: Who... what? Dear lord, you've been lied to. She could have killed her lover and lied to everyone! She's not the most *faire and juste* at all, she's smoke and mirrors and will-o-wisps!

fields.Title: You: ""What's going on? What did you do?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What's going on? What did you do?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Industrial espionage. I joined a b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Industrial espionage. I joined a business collective with the intention of betraying them. I did my job well enough to be asked to do it again."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""That doesn't really work, does it?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That doesn't really work, does it?" She has almost devoured the cigarette she lit. She looks at it sadly. "Not without a drink to wash it down..."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Yeah, it was a real *motherfucker*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, it was a real *motherfucker*... ouch..." She looks down. Her cigarette has singed her fingers.
fields.Alternate1: "Yeah, it was a real *motherfucker*." She immediately lights another one.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She looks down with a wince. Her ci..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She looks down with a wince. Her cigarette has singed her fingers.
fields.Alternate1: "Sure." She immediately lights another one.

fields.Title: Logic: "Coming up with a theory. She said R..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Coming up with a theory. She said Ruby *knew* something was wrong before she said anything. How come? It was loud downstairs, she couldn't have heard the shot...

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Well, Ruby said let's talk upstair..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Well, Ruby said let's talk upstairs. I showed her the room... I've known these people since December, they know my situation. That I can't leave a paper trail. Ruby was the first one I told..."

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "This is concurrent with your doubts..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is concurrent with your doubts -- at the autopsy -- about the colouring being...

fields.Title: Logic: "He was a serviceman -- he must have..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He was a serviceman -- he must have had a gun. Somewhere, lying around. Close to her hand...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant gives you a sideways..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant gives you a sideways glance.

fields.Title: Volition: "Look who's waking up from a thousan..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look who's waking up from a thousand years of sleep!

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Or... I don't know anything anymor..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Or... I don't know anything anymore. All I do is wait here." She looks at the table.

fields.Title: You: ""I don't think so. Why did you do i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't think so. Why did you do it?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Uhm..." The lieutenant glances at..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Uhm..." The lieutenant glances at you -- then at the door.

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "That *is* the Emergencies Desk numb..."
fields.Dialogue Text: That *is* the Emergencies Desk number...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Why would they do that?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why would they do that?"

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "You almost say the words, then stop..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You almost say the words, then stop -- the lieutenant is off somewhere, 28 kilometres from here, probably reading the *manual* for incarceration. The one he *knows how to use*. Come back and say this with Kim here; you can't handle it without him.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She's silent for a second -- as if..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She's silent for a second -- as if looking into herself for certainty. Then, in a hushed voice, she says...

fields.Title: You: ""What do you mean, *like*?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you mean, *like*?"

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "She's not really sure. It *was* rig..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She's not really sure. It *was* right above the bed -- she could have seen all sorts of things from there.

fields.Title: Volition: "Her! Stop letting her distract you."
fields.Dialogue Text: Her! Stop letting her distract you.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Thank you." She cradles herself fo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thank you." She cradles herself for warmth. "Thank you. You won't regret it."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I will escort you to the motor car..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I will escort you to the motor carriage outside, miss."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I won't, sir..." She exhales, shak..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I won't, sir..." She exhales, shaking visibly. Then she collects herself.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He puts the handcuffs away. "These..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He puts the handcuffs away. "These won't be necessary. I will take you to Station 57 myself -- and slow the extradition process as much as I can."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It may be possible to stall it ind..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It may be possible to stall it indefinitely. But you *will* be safer there for the purposes of this investigation." He turns to you.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I *did* -- I also had a side job s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I *did* -- I also had a side job selling insurance that I was really good at. Got picked up by a bank. *Competitive intelligence*, they called it."

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "Wait, wait, everyone -- just *wait*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wait, wait, everyone -- just *wait*. What is this? Derail this whole thing immediately and *investigate*.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""How do you deal with anything? It'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "How do you deal with anything? It's all just..." She looks at you with pleading eyes. "How do *you* do it?"

fields.Title: Volition: "I can't restrain this one. The need..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I can't restrain this one. The need to *cop* is too strong. You just need to ask it.

fields.Title: Volition: "There is something suspicious about..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There is something suspicious about that theory, but you can't put your finger on it.

fields.Title: You: ""It's okay if you did it in self de..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's okay if you did it in self defence."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I promise I will be right here all..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I promise I will be right here all the time -- nights too. I'll help you *any* way I can in this investigation and I *will* be at Station 41 in six weeks." She repeats. "I promise."

fields.Title: Empathy: "The conference centres... the peopl..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The conference centres... the people who are angry at her. Her past.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""As to who hired me for the job --..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "As to who hired me for the job -- I don't know. But *they're* after me too. Along with Looskap, and their friends in the MI." She breathes out, heavily. "Once you're done in the competitive intelligence circuit, you don't have allies. You're radioactive."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""He was heavy. I pushed him off and..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He was heavy. I pushed him off and he fell to the floor -- there." She points through the window. "He only had his boots on. I bit the pillow... not to scream, then ran downstairs..." There's a long pause. She just stands there, her arms at her sides.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""He was still on the floor. Slouche..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He was still on the floor. Slouched. I couldn't be there with him anymore. So I ran down -- and out of my room. Into the hallway. Down the stairs. I knew there would be people there."

fields.Title: Drama: "You *may* sometimes be bad at readi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You *may* sometimes be bad at reading her, but this time, truly -- she's telling you how it really went down.

fields.Title: Hand/Eye Coordination: "Another hit. The lieutenant looks a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Another hit. The lieutenant looks at you -- in acknowledgement.

fields.Title: You: "Better not to remark."
fields.Dialogue Text: Better not to remark.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She nods."
fields.Dialogue Text: She nods.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I've said I'm sorry. What more do..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I've said I'm sorry. What more do you want me to say? I did my best not to lie. It didn't always work."

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "She has the training for it. Two, m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She has the training for it. Two, maybe three years of self defence? Her body is hard and lean underneath that jump suit...

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "It's not one of respect. You may wa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's not one of respect. You may want to add a clever *retort* to this one.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Like what?" She waits, her light b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Like what?" She waits, her light brown eyes wandering... over the floor... over your face...

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "You should have a look at that wind..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You should have a look at that window -- reconstruct the scene. It's right here, so near...

fields.Title: Shivers: "Long, spindly arms are spinning the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Long, spindly arms are spinning the buoy around, turning it, inspecting it like a magic eight-ball, trying to find a way to snap it open...

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""A teenage boy. A million years ago.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "A teenage boy. A million years ago."

fields.Title: Drama: "Okay, he's too busy doing something..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Okay, he's too busy doing something else now. I meant Rhetoric. Anyway, don't listen to that guy -- we're right, she's saintly. Carry on.

fields.Title: You: ""Kim, arrest this woman before she..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Kim, arrest this woman before she can say anything else." (Ignore her theory.)

fields.Title: You: ""What is it?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What is it?"

fields.Title: Savoir Faire: "Then slipped back downstairs withou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Then slipped back downstairs without anyone noticing? That *is* possible...

fields.Title: Volition: "That's it. I'm calling it. Kim is b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: That's it. I'm calling it. Kim is beyond compromised.

fields.Title: You: ""I do like the sound of that... ano..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I do like the sound of that... another Revachol. Free. Independent."

fields.Title: Drama: "If you have doubts, just give us *o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: If you have doubts, just give us *one* example of deceit! Just one, and we will gladly change our minds.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Before we do..." He turns to her,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Before we do..." He turns to her, the cuffs still in his hand. "What exactly in your relationship made you think she's romantically interested in you?"

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "No, wait! Look at her! Teeth like p..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No, wait! Look at her! Teeth like pearls, face like a pebble -- she looks like a Twenties movie star. You can almost see her in Automatik Polychrome. Those posters in Ruby's lorry...

fields.Title: You: ""I've made my choice." (Decide what..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I've made my choice." (Decide what to do with her.)

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""You answer to the Coalition Govern..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You answer to the Coalition Government -- and, by extension, the *Moralintern*..." She reaches for a new cigarette.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "The young woman looks at her cigare..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The young woman looks at her cigarette -- with melancholy. It's almost gone.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""No -- not just yet." He turns to t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No -- not just yet." He turns to the woman. "Who is *Ruby*?"

fields.Title: Jump to: [You: ""Before we continue -- who is Ruby?""]
Suggestion: "It could have been a *desire* murde..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It could have been a *desire* murder. Maybe an act of jealousy?

fields.Title: You: ""You *lied* to us, miss.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You *lied* to us, miss."

fields.Title: You: ""You don't look surprised. You were..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You don't look surprised. You were expecting this."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I know that. But the people around..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I know that. But the people around here -- they don't see it that way. And if I am to stay here I need to get along with them."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""What happens if they do?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What happens if they do?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""What *exactly* did you do?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What *exactly* did you do?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I don't." She shrugs. "How do *you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't." She shrugs. "How do *you* live with yourself?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""That's okay." He makes a note. "We..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That's okay." He makes a note. "Were you inebriated?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""It took Ruby maybe half an hour to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It took Ruby maybe half an hour to come back with Titus. I'd gotten him ready by then, they carried him out. I knew what they were going to do -- make it look like a hanging. Ruby said they would."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Yes.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes."

fields.Title: Drama: "Who hath told you these *lies*? She..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Who hath told you these *lies*? She was merely confused by the esoteric arts you deploy in policework.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I don't know. I haven't seen her s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know. I haven't seen her since."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Thursday night. It was late. Some..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thursday night. It was late. Some time after twelve."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""But I know the *time* of the call..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "But I know the *time* of the call too!" She breathes in. "I know I have not been 100% truthful with you, officers. But I *am* now."

fields.Title: Half Light: "Tighten it. You've got her."
fields.Dialogue Text: Tighten it. You've got her.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""What?" Her nails tap on the steel..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What?" Her nails tap on the steel railing, nervously. The sound of cold metal ringing under the wind.

fields.Title: You: ""I should have guessed. You don't l..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I should have guessed. You don't look Oranjese."

fields.Title: You: ""I'll keep calling you Klaasje. "(P..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'll keep calling you Klaasje. "(Proceed.)

fields.Title: You: ""You're a flight risk -- and I've a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're a flight risk -- and I've already told you're a *suspect* in a murder investigation, remember?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""No.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""No." She shrugs it off. "No -- why..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No." She shrugs it off. "No -- why would she do that to herself? No, I just remembered you told me about it, and..."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""*Still...*" she says, her voice br..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "*Still...*" she says, her voice breaking. "After all this. Sir, please... it's a shitty world and I know I'm shitty too, I know..." Her hand turns into a fist, slowly, crushing the cigarette she's still holding.

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "The light refracts. She takes out h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The light refracts. She takes out her lighter.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant makes a note of it."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant makes a note of it.

fields.Title: Volition: "It's ominous -- you buying into her..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's ominous -- you buying into her theory and running with it. Be careful with this Logic guy.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""She could have come to the roof th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She could have come to the roof through that, then made the shot right here, where I stand. It was dark outside, I wouldn't have seen her."

fields.Title: Authority: "Don't arrest her. Push her a bit mo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Don't arrest her. Push her a bit more but then let her off. That Ruby theory was solid. (And she's beautiful.)

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It's okay. Tell us as much as you'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's okay. Tell us as much as you're comfortable with." He waits for her to continue.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "Good thinking. Clear your head. You..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Good thinking. Clear your head. You should clear *your* head... get into his mindset.

fields.Title: You: ""Why *did* you waste my time then?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why *did* you waste my time then? If you knew I would find out."

fields.Title: You: ""Tell me *exactly* what happened.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tell me *exactly* what happened."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""The leader? Of what?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "The leader? Of what?"

fields.Title: You: ""The occult vision was right. He wa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The occult vision was right. He was enjoying the moment of his death."

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "Wait-- the Hardie boys said she'd v..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wait-- the Hardie boys said she'd visited them last week. Glen and...

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I thought officers in Revachol wou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I thought officers in Revachol would be more enlightened about these things." She looks you in the eye. "Especially since you've admitted to taking drugs yourself."

fields.Title: You: ""It probably didn't.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "It probably didn't."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""He kept throwing stones at him for..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He kept throwing stones at him for *three days*. I could hear the *thud*, *thud*..." She shakes her head. "So I called you. I hope with all my heart it's not the last thing I do in Revachol."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She nods, silently. She doesn't eve..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She nods, silently. She doesn't even smoke, just picks up the cold coffee and holds it in her hands.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I don't..." She squints. "How did..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't..." She squints. "How did you know that?"

fields.Title: You: "I remember doubting she made the ca..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I remember doubting she made the call she said she made. To the police.

fields.Title: Drama: "Seditious talk! That was not even O..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Seditious talk! That was not even Our Wise Council, it was this shithead! This one. The next one.

fields.Title: Drama: "Your paranoia is unflattering. She..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your paranoia is unflattering. She has been nothing but forthcoming and you're staring mutely into her face like a donkey!

fields.Title: You: ""You're probably not even Miss Oran..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're probably not even Miss Oranje '37, are you?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""It's useless.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's useless."

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "Of course -- she doesn't look like..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Of course -- she doesn't look like an Oranjese woman at all. She's...

fields.Title: You: ""Who was he?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who was he?"

fields.Title: Empathy: "Gearing up for this betrayal is har..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Gearing up for this betrayal is hard for her.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "What she's saying is -- sex?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What she's saying is -- sex?

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I do not." He turns to her, the cu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I do not." He turns to her, the cuffs still in his hand. "What exactly about your relationship with this person made you think she's romantically interested in you?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Yes." She nods."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes." She nods.

fields.Title: You: ""I also find it hard to believe.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I also find it hard to believe."

fields.Title: Volition: "This guy won't budge. You have to w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This guy won't budge. You have to wake  Multi-Face up -- forcefully -- if you want to continue pushing her.

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "Well, I'll be damned! That's one mo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Well, I'll be damned! That's one more thing we know about the world!

fields.Title: Logic: "Could it be that Ruby was cleaning..."

fields.Dialogue Text: "That's a lot of shit you've gotten yourself into."

fields.Title: You: ""By not remembering a single god da..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "By not remembering a single god damn thing."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Nothing. I was trapped. I was stuc..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Nothing. I was trapped. I was stuck in my room -- downstairs. I got some clothes on and crawled back up, drew the blinds. Blood was coming from his mouth -- not a lot. Just a little."

fields.Title: You: ""What time was this?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What time was this?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""What does that mean?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What does that mean?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""What? Fucking themselves over for..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What? Fucking themselves over for no reason? This is not what happened, officer."

fields.Title: Logic: "He was a serviceman. He must have h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He was a serviceman. He must have had a gun lying around. Close to her hand -- a  military weapon using *jacketed ammunition*.

fields.Title: You: ""Why?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why?"

fields.Title: You: "Say nothing."
fields.Dialogue Text: Say nothing.

fields.Title: Volition: "...or should we arrest her? She's a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: ...or should we arrest her? She's a flight risk and she lied to you -- she should be taken into custody.

fields.Title: You: ""'Okay' what?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "'Okay' what?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She nods. Her round eyes meet yours..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She nods. Her round eyes meet yours. They seem moist from the wind on the roof.

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "Take it easy. Start at the top, cho..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Take it easy. Start at the top, choose at the bottom, it's how we've always done it. No rush...

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "She purposefully misrepresented inf..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She purposefully misrepresented information crucial to the case.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Ruby.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Ruby."

fields.Title: You: ""And *how* could she have killed hi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "And *how* could she have killed him?"

fields.Title: You: ""I don't understand. Ruby's a woman..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't understand. Ruby's a woman, right? It's a *woman's* name."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Interesting theory. Did she know t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Interesting theory. Did she know that door exists? Had you been out here -- with her?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I can do this on my own. She's not..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I can do this on my own. She's not an immediate flight risk. See you tomorrow morning, officer. Downstairs, at the Whirling-in-Rags."
fields.Alternate1: "I can do this on my own. She's not an immediate flight risk. See you tomorrow morning, officer. Downstairs, at the Whirling-in-Rags. Or outside your shack."

fields.Title: Empathy: "There is desperation there -- in th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There is desperation there -- in that silence. A cornered animal looking for a way out.

fields.Title: You: ""This has got nothing to do with an..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This has got nothing to do with anything."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""You're welcome to it. It's in the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're welcome to it. It's in the reeds northwest of here, past a broken sewage pipe. Right near the waterline."

fields.Title: Jump to: [Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""She said she's in love with me. Sh..."]
Electrochemistry: "Look at her: teeth like pearls, fac..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look at her: teeth like pearls, face like a pebble -- she looks like a Twenties movie star. You can almost see her in Automatik Polychrome. Those posters in Ruby's lorry...

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She looks at you in silence, her fa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She looks at you in silence, her face filled with fear, lips parted...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""If you knew we would find out even..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "If you knew we would find out eventually -- why *did* you waste our time?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""They will kill me, officer. If you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "They will kill me, officer. If you file my name, take me in for questioning, enter me into the Moralintern mill..."

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "Wait -- Titus said she was gurning..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Wait -- Titus said she was gurning her jaw off. Much more than usual.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Oh yeah..." She tilts her head. "I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh yeah..." She tilts her head. "I did one of his lines. Just to clear my head."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Why not.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why not."

fields.Title: You: "In her bedroom, inside?"
fields.Dialogue Text: In her bedroom, inside?

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I understand." She puts her coffee..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I understand." She puts her coffee mug on the table.

fields.Title: You: ""I don't answer to *anyone*. Mother..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't answer to *anyone*. Mother fucking anyone, butch."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She nods. "You share a database wit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She nods. "You share a database with them. You send people to their courts." She lights the cigarette.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Wow. Someone has their testosteron..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wow. Someone has their testosterone cranked up to neolithic. Let me just forcefully re-rail this talk for you, okay? Are you okay with that? Here we go..."

fields.Title: You: ""I think we're done here -- for now..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I think we're done here -- for now." (Conclude.)

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "Looskap -- these people engineer fi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Looskap -- these people engineer financial disasters in second world countries. The conglomerate also includes The Bank of Consecration, Eeirberg and the popular Pappa Lollo line of dairy products.

fields.Title: You: ""Who did you do this to? And on who..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who did you do this to? And on whose behalf?"

fields.Title: Empathy: "Out of guilt."
fields.Dialogue Text: Out of guilt.

fields.Title: You: ""What did you do then?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What did you do then?"

fields.Title: You: ""I knew he enjoyed the moment he di..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I knew he enjoyed the moment he died. I could see it in him."

fields.Title: You: ""I could see it in his eyes.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I could see it in his eyes."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Yes. Ruby said the blood in him......"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes. Ruby said the blood in him... would look like a hanging."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She's silent. Just looks at her cig..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She's silent. Just looks at her cigarette.

fields.Title: You: ""You *have* the training for it. I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You *have* the training for it. I can see it in your posture, your shoulders..."

fields.Title: You: ""I do drugs to keep working, cleani..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I do drugs to keep working, cleaning up this *shit* you've created here."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "Her shoulders do not shake, despite..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Her shoulders do not shake, despite the strength it takes to keep herself from crying.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We can't go after Looskap. Not yet..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We can't go after Looskap. Not yet. There are other, saner leads."

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "*If they want to kill me, they'll k..."
fields.Dialogue Text: *If they want to kill me, they'll kill me. If they want to toy with me they will*. She's come to this conclusion weeks ago.

fields.Title: You: ""This Ruby -- where is this Ruby no..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This Ruby -- where is this Ruby now?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Okay." She puts her coffee mug on..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay." She puts her coffee mug on the table.

fields.Title: Drama: "Gosh, she's so young, isn't she? Sh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Gosh, she's so young, isn't she? She would look spectacular in a *starring role*!

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""West of the boardwalk -- in the re..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "West of the boardwalk -- in the reeds -- on the coast there." She points toward a clump of  ruins on the western horizon. "I put it there when I first arrived. Haven't been there since. I'm not sure I could even find it now..."

fields.Title: You: ""Why?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""You can call me whatever you want...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You can call me whatever you want." She smiles, too tired to laugh.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""But I haven't *done* anything..."..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "But I haven't *done* anything..." She backs up against the railing -- with a forced smile on her face. "Anything *illegal*."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She slowly-slowly lights another ci..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She slowly-slowly lights another cigarette and steadies her breath. As if in the presence of some tiger.

fields.Title: You: ""Cute. You're still under arrest.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cute. You're still under arrest."

fields.Title: You: ""And what is that?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "And what is that?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I don't understand." The lieutenan..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't understand." The lieutenant sounds incredulous. He still has the cuffs in his hand. "What exactly in your relationship made you think she's romantically interested in you?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Okay." She looks relieved."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay." She looks relieved.

fields.Title: Jump to: [Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""*Still...*" she says, her voice br..."]
You: ""What *other* option do I have?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What *other* option do I have?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""You have those *station calls*, ri..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You have those *station calls*, right? Where I have to show up at the station or I'll become a fugitive. You can write me one. You don't have to take me in right now... I promise I won't go out anymore, at night. I'll be right here."

fields.Title: You: ""I'll let you off the hook -- for n..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'll let you off the hook -- for now. Don't make me regret it." (Don't arrest her.)

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Don't. The world can change. It ha..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't. The world can change. It has changed before..." She looks at you, frozen to her spot.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""When he was shot?" She thinks. "I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "When he was shot?" She thinks. "I may have. I don't know. I couldn't hear anything over the glass exploding."

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "The gunshot wasn't that loud? This..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The gunshot wasn't that loud? This is something to keep in mind when assessing the distance of the shot.

fields.Title: You: ""You said you studied *Oranjese lit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You said you studied *Oranjese lit*. What is with this fugitive stuff?"

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "The grand expanse of water is barel..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The grand expanse of water is barely visible in the darkness of the night. The horizon is there, somewhere...

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""She could have come up through the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She could have come up through there, then taken the shot -- right here, where I stand. It was too dark outside, I wouldn't have seen her."

fields.Title: Volition: "Here we go. For once you seem to ha..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Here we go. For once you seem to have her off-guard.

fields.Title: Volition: "Nothing to do with her? You'll be t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Nothing to do with her? You'll be the judge of that.

fields.Title: You: ""Did you hear or see the shooter --..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Did you hear or see the shooter -- at any point?"

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "Still you see the glass sparkling o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Still you see the glass sparkling out of the corner of your eye...

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I didn't lie. Not a lot. I've done..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I didn't lie. Not a lot. I've done my absolute best *not* to. I just..."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I turned back to him." She breathe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I turned back to him." She breathes out. A moment's silence. "His eyes were looking through me and his mouth was open, dumb... I could see... I could..."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Sylvie was tending the bar." She l..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sylvie was tending the bar." She looks down. "A lot of people were there. The Hardies were at the table in front of the stage, I think the Union box was full..."

fields.Title: Authority: "This Ruby, in her phrasing, is entr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This Ruby, in her phrasing, is entrusted with great power. She trusts her. So do the others.

fields.Title: Suggestion: "What are you trying to be -- tactfu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What are you trying to be -- tactful? She wouldn't mind. Go on then...

fields.Title: Hand/Eye Coordination: "A direct hit. The lieutenant looks..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A direct hit. The lieutenant looks at you -- in acknowledgement."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""What?" She gathers the last vestig..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What?" She gathers the last vestiges of her strength. "Why would I put myself through this... insanity? Get myself cornered like this?" There's a silence.

fields.Title: You: ""You know what I mean. Do drugs mak..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You know what I mean. Do drugs make you aggressive?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She simply shakes her head."
fields.Dialogue Text: She simply shakes her head.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She pinches the filter of her cigar..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She pinches the filter of her cigarette, hard. Then looks at you.

fields.Title: You: ""And?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "And?"

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "He's thinking -- *are* we done here..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's thinking -- *are* we done here, or...?

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "It's a Graad name -- Zsiemsk or Yug..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's a Graad name -- Zsiemsk or Yugo-Graad in origin -- not Occidental at all. Smells of motor oil, taiga, economic desolation, and rock music infused alcoholism.

fields.Title: You: ""Wait, Klaasje is an abbreviation o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wait, Klaasje is an abbreviation of Katarzine Alasije?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""It was my first real boyfriend who..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It was my first real boyfriend who gave me that name. He never recovered from the shit we went through. Because of me."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""And more." She nods. "I made the m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "And more." She nods. "I made the mistake of confiding in her -- I told her I was on the run. She started *protecting* me. It became an unhealthy relationship."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Somehow she *knew* Lely was dead...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Somehow she *knew* Lely was dead. She wasn't surprised at all. When we came up here she was calm as a stone too. She cleaned it all up, like she had a... plan."

fields.Title: Volition: "Something tells you: you will."
fields.Dialogue Text: Something tells you: you will.

fields.Title: You: ""Let's write you a Station Call. If..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Let's write you a Station Call. If you miss it -- I can't help you anymore." (Write a Station Call.)
fields.Alternate1: "Let's write you a Station Call, Katarzine. If you miss it -- I can't help you anymore." (Write a Station Call.)
fields.Alternate2: "Let's write you a Station Call, Klaasje. If you miss it -- I can't help you anymore." (Write a Station Call.)
fields.Alternate3: "Let's write you a Station Call, Miss Oranje. If you miss it -- I can't help you anymore." (Write a Station Call.)

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""The world can change. It's changed..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The world can change. It's changed before." Her round light brown eyes shining with tears.

fields.Title: Drama: "That's not the answer she was hopin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: That's not the answer she was hoping for. Thought that you were some kind of patriot, or communard, did she?

fields.Title: You: ""Not on my watch.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Not on my watch."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I find that hard to believe, miss...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I find that hard to believe, miss." The handcuffs jingle in his hands...

fields.Title: You: "What was that feeling?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What was that feeling?

fields.Title: Volition: "It looks like this one's not waking..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It looks like this one's not waking up. You'll have to do it without pushing her further. At least for now.

fields.Title: Volition: "This one's *still* not budging. You..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This one's *still* not budging. You'll have to do it without pushing her further.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""You're right... there's more.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're right... there's more."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I..." She looks down, then into yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I..." She looks down, then into your eyes. "One of them killed themselves. Because of me."

fields.Title: Suggestion: "Of course. This case takes preceden..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Of course. This case takes precedence.

fields.Title: Composure: "Her chest rises and falls with each..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Her chest rises and falls with each word. She keeps herself together, and says it...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""How could we have *missed* that......"
fields.Dialogue Text: "How could we have *missed* that..." He shakes his head. "And when was the tampering -- twenty minutes after death?"

fields.Title: Half Light: "You *are*. This is not the end of t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You *are*. This is not the end of this.

fields.Title: You: ""That's all good, but I think we sh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That's all good, but I think we should still take you in -- just in case." (Step a little bit closer.)

fields.Title: Volition: "Okay? And WHAT?!?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Okay? And WHAT?!?

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "The pale. The Mundi isola. The Occi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The pale. The Mundi isola. The Occident. And then -- *Oranje*. The Old Old World.

fields.Title: You: ""You're right. This is bad. You've..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're right. This is bad. You've destroyed what people have built."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I do that too, yes. It's unbelieva..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I do that too, yes. It's unbelievably effective. Especially when combined with cigarettes. And drugs."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Okay..." She takes a deep breath...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay..." She takes a deep breath. "He was in a kneeling position, he had just entered me. I was on my back, looking at him. I heard the window behind me shatter and I turned to look -- there was a hole in the glass..."

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "A great pain moves through her, a d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A great pain moves through her, a dark and indefinite wave. She continues in spite of it.

fields.Title: You: ""Then what happened?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Then what happened?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Ruby was there too. They were havi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Ruby was there too. They were having such a good time..." She pauses. "I sat down and they all welcomed me. I didn't even have to say anything, Ruby *knew* something was wrong."

fields.Title: Volition: "What are you doing?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What are you doing?

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Yes.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes."

fields.Title: You: ""So my feeling was right earlier. H..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So my feeling was right earlier. He *was* enjoying the moment of his death."

fields.Title: You: ""That's enough. I had another quest..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That's enough. I had another question."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Do drugs make you aggressive?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do drugs make you aggressive?"

fields.Title: Half Light: "Rage? Who knows the *dark currents*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Rage? Who knows the *dark currents* where lovers go?

fields.Title: You: ""Clever retort.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Clever retort."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I thought they'd found me. They've..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I thought they'd found me. They've killed him to punish me.... All last week I've tried not to talk to anyone, or be seen with anyone..." She looks at her cigarette.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I don't ask you to, lieutenant. If..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't ask you to, lieutenant. If there's one thing I know it's that you'll get *nothing* from there."

fields.Title: You: ""When was the window changed?" (Poi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "When was the window changed?" (Point to it.)

fields.Title: You: "She was *confused* when I asked abo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She was *confused* when I asked about the bullet in his head. That was a lie.

fields.Title: Suggestion: "Try not to sweat so profusely in he..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Try not to sweat so profusely in her presence too. You'll blow your chances.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Like I lied before. Like I lied to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Like I lied before. Like I lied to my employers. I have to lie *all the time*..." She looks at her hands, her fingernails are chipped white. "I'm so tired of it."
fields.Alternate1: "Like I lied before. Like I did at LCSB... I have to lie *all the time*." She looks at her hands, her fingernails are chipped white. "I'm so tired of it."

fields.Title: Empathy: "You sense a little hesitation there..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You sense a little hesitation there -- or maybe even fear? The stress was on the wrong syllable.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She stands before you, holding her..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She stands before you, holding her back very straight.

fields.Title: You: ""Enough." (Conclude.)"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Enough." (Conclude.)

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Falsified documents?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Falsified documents?"

fields.Title: You: ""Where is this buoy?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Where is this buoy?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""It's Katarzine Alasije." The smile..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's Katarzine Alasije." The smile on her face is timid -- almost painfully so.

fields.Title: Drama: "That's right. Stern and merciless n..."
fields.Dialogue Text: That's right. Stern and merciless now, STERN AND MERCILESS as we reel her in.
fields.Alternate1: That's right, gang. Stern and merciless now -- STERN AND MERCILESS as we reel her in.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""When I started spending time with..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "When I started spending time with Lely," she says in a near-whisper, "she told me to end it. Said there would be *shit* if I didn't. It was not a good meeting. We stopped talking after that, but..."

fields.Title: You: ""But... you're *also* a woman.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "But... you're *also* a woman."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""She came over one night. Drunk. Sa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She came over one night. Drunk. Said she'd turn my life into a *living hell*. I've been threatened before, so I can tell when someone *knows* how to do it."

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "The peephole!"
fields.Dialogue Text: The peephole!

fields.Title: Drama: "Don't let your imagination run wild..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Don't let your imagination run wild here, sire. Keep it on track.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I don't know..." She throws away t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know..." She throws away the cigarette. "To spend my days with smoke and drink and dance -- wallowing in shit. Just like everyone else."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""You do have the form..." He looks..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You do have the form..." He looks at your ledger.

fields.Title: Drama: "This may have been a *grave* mistak..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This may have been a *grave* mistake, sire.

fields.Title: Shivers: "A free Revachol... There is a low,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A free Revachol... There is a low, distant rumble on the motor tract. A great machine, shaking the pillars down south. Electricity runs up your spine.

fields.Title: You: ""West of the boardwalk, in the reed..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "West of the boardwalk, in the reeds? I need to check this buoy out." (Accept task.)
fields.Alternate1: "West of the boardwalk, in the reeds? We have to check this buoy out." (Accept task.)

fields.Title: You: ""Chill. I'm the cool cop, remember?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Chill. I'm the cool cop, remember?"

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "Samaran boxing, or Sam Bo. Graceful..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Samaran boxing, or Sam Bo. Graceful martial arts stuff -- stealth, cleverness, and cool.

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "Oops..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Oops...

fields.Title: Logic: "She did, of course."
fields.Dialogue Text: She did, of course.

fields.Title: You: ""You sent us on a run-around.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You sent us on a run-around."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I knew there was a chance you'd ge..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I knew there was a chance you'd get them to tell you. It's what you do. You're the police."

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "A grand expanse of water reaches ov..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A grand expanse of water reaches over the bay and to the horizon. Grey and pale violet in the morning light...

fields.Title: You: "What lies beyond it?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What lies beyond it?

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She smiles, cautiously. "I wish it..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She smiles, cautiously. "I wish it did. But sadly no."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Officer. Regain control of yoursel..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Officer. Regain control of yourself." He turns to the woman: "What does our *limited cooperation* with the Moralintern have to do with this?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""This was not a joke. Real people l..."

fields.Dialogue Text: True, sire. 'Tis true.

fields.Title: Empathy: "She fears an arrest right here and..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She fears an arrest right here and now. This has been an awful turn of events for her.

fields.Title: Drama: "She definitely called the cops. Tha..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She definitely called the cops. That was *task complete*. It could not hath been a *lie*. That is impossible.

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "Let the miss speak. She's tall and..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Let the miss speak. She's tall and thin and tired -- a twig trying so hard not to break...

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Because of the Hardies -- I couldn..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Because of the Hardies -- I couldn't just dispense with them, they were only trying to help me." She looks at her feet. "Out of the shit I'd gotten into."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""It was a mistake." She winces. "I'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It was a mistake." She winces. "I'm sorry for wasting your time."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I am not. There is more here, miss.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I am not. There is more here, miss."

fields.Title: You: ""What did you do to have these *peo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What did you do to have these *people* after you?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""It's not nice -- but it's not ille..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's not nice -- but it's not illegal, not here in Revachol. Or even in Oranje."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I need the names of the companies..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I need the names of the companies involved. And who hired you." He taps on his notebook.

fields.Title: You: ""I do drugs.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I do drugs."

fields.Title: You: ""Were you inebriated?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Were you inebriated?"

fields.Title: Logic: "Interesting. Why did this Ruby go t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Interesting. Why did this Ruby go through so much trouble -- to hide something someone *else* did? Look into this later!

fields.Title: You: ""Did you *party* with Ruby too?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Did you *party* with Ruby too?"

fields.Title: You: ""Downstairs people have this *crazy..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Downstairs people have this *crazy* idea that you killed him."

fields.Title: You: ""Do you want to hit me right now?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you want to hit me right now?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Because life is hell, officer," sh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Because life is hell, officer," she finds refuge in her cigarette. It's thin, but it's something.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""So they wouldn't be hurt. I've com..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So they wouldn't be hurt. I've come to understand, however -- this is paranoia. What happened didn't have anything to do with me."

fields.Title: You: ""I *know* you didn't make the call.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I *know* you didn't make the call."

fields.Title: Conceptualization: "She sounds like a sixth grader, apo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She sounds like a sixth grader, apologizing.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I haven't said it aloud in such a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I haven't said it aloud in such a long time... that name." She shakes her head.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I know I'm shit -- I know. But I h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I know I'm shit -- I know. But I haven't done anything. At least nothing illegal."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She nods, nervously. Then pulls on..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She nods, nervously. Then pulls on her cigarette.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""We spent a lot of time together. L..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We spent a lot of time together. Listening to the radio and such. She had great milieus. And she was good company. I was sorry it had to end..." She pauses.

fields.Title: Drama: "What are you talking about? She's a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What are you talking about? She's afraid you'll *arrest* her.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""You mean to suggest -- she made it?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You mean to suggest -- she made it?"

fields.Title: Volition: "Maybe. Maybe not. Mercy is rarely a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Maybe. Maybe not. Mercy is rarely a *complete* mistake.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Maybe Revachol could be free? I co..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Maybe Revachol could be free? I could be tried in a free Revachol? An independent state that doesn't hand its detainees over to the Moralintern."

fields.Title: Shivers: "IT'S COMING."
fields.Dialogue Text: IT'S COMING.

fields.Title: Drama: "Her political overture has succeede..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Her political overture has succeeded, we see?

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Of course." She nods."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Of course." She nods.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""She could have come to the roof th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She could have come to the roof through that, then taken the shot -- right here, where I stand. It was dark outside, I wouldn't have seen her."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Would you say she is the..." He lo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Would you say she is the..." He looks at you. "Eighth Hardie boy?"

fields.Title: You: ""Relax. One more thing.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Relax. One more thing."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""No." She shakes her head. "People..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No." She shakes her head. "People don't take drugs to kill each other -- they take them to feel okay with each other."

fields.Title: Drama: "She probably didn't give you her re..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She probably didn't give you her real name either -- why would she? Arrest her immediately, before she further entangles you in her *web of lies*!

fields.Title: Drama: "Very good, sire. She will never adm..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Very good, sire. She will never admit to it, but we can *see* that she didn't.

fields.Title: You: "(Now that Kim's here) "What if I to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Now that Kim's here) "What if I told you you're under arrest, miss."
fields.Alternate1: (Now that Kim's here) "What if I told you you're under arrest, Katarzine Alasije?"
fields.Alternate2: (Now that Kim's here) "What if I told you you're under arrest, Klaasje?"
fields.Alternate3: (Now that Kim's here) "What if I told you you're under arrest, Miss Oranje Disco Dancer?"

fields.Title: Volition: "Oh god. That was a lie too. Who mad..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Oh god. That was a lie too. Who made the call then?

fields.Title: Drama: "Look at her! Her hands, her nails,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look at her! Her hands, her nails, the cigarette... Every second you stall, you become more entangled in this spider's *web of lies*. Arrest her immediately!
fields.Alternate1: She probably didn't make the god damn call either -- why would she? She was too busy abusing morphine and *cocainum!* Arrest her immediately!

fields.Title: You: ""Is that why you're looking over yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Is that why you're looking over your shoulder? You're afraid of the Moralintern?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I am. I am a destroyer. People los..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I am. I am a destroyer. People lost their jobs -- good people. Not just C-Suite assholes. And the way I got into accounting..." She shakes her head at the thought.

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "You have it in you to be a champion..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You have it in you to be a champion. Keep your head in the game now...

fields.Title: You: ""You were tampering with the body.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You were tampering with the body."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Ruby went outside to talk to Titus..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Ruby went outside to talk to Titus and the boys. I was just... looking at Lely. In the bathroom. I had to put his clothes back on. His armour too. It was tough, but I've seen him take it off and put it on many times."

fields.Title: Half Light: "She's fought outside that *gym* of..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She's fought outside that *gym* of hers. That much is clear. Moreover -- she would like to do it now: hit you. It's in her shoulders...

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I thought Revachol would be more e..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I thought Revachol would be more enlightened about this." She looks you in the eye. "Especially since you've taken them yourself."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I thought you Revachol people woul..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I thought you Revachol people would be more enlightened on this..." She pauses. "I'm sorry, officer. I'm under some stress here."

fields.Title: Drama: "But we *are* awake, sire! She has b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: But we *are* awake, sire! She has been forthcoming -- with sordid details women usually conceal! Most *shocking* details of the sexual kind! We are a bulwark, un-breached...
fields.Alternate1: We are *still* wide awake and staring into an archipelago of truths! Scandalous facts she's shared, omitting nothing, even if it casts her as a demimonde with *sexually lax* morals...

fields.Title: Drama: "Who is this *personhood* picking th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Who is this *personhood* picking these seditious options? Can't you see the detective grows weary of your malcontent?!

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "He's thinking -- *are* we done here..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's thinking -- *are* we done here?

fields.Title: Drama: "Anyone could know that, sire. By lo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Anyone could know that, sire. By looking around and calling the desk. I don't believe a single word she says!

fields.Title: You: ""You're a suspect in a murder inves..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're a suspect in a murder investigation. You're a flight risk. That is all the reason I need."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She nods, then nervously pulls on h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She nods, then nervously pulls on her cigarette.

fields.Title: You: ""Sounds like she was fixated on you.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sounds like she was fixated on you."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I know you can do that -- just let..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I know you can do that -- just let me come in on my own. In two months. Or maybe even one month. That's all I need..."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I agree." The lieutenant turns to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I agree." The lieutenant turns to her. "You wouldn't give us your real name -- not when people are after you."

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "Why? She told us some pretty intere..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Why? She told us some pretty interesting things there.

fields.Title: You: ""More?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "More?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It's a shame we never got around t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's a shame we never got around to doing a thorough autopsy..." He shakes his head. "And when was the tampering -- twenty minutes after death?"

fields.Title: You: ""Cool. I'm satisfied with this expl..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cool. I'm satisfied with this explanation."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She pulls on the cigarette, looking..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She pulls on the cigarette, looking up at the sky. Her hair ripples in the breeze as she stands there, silent.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""The job was Loosduin County Saving..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The job was Loosduin County Savings Bank -- they sound small but they're part of the Looskap conglomerate. That was the second job. The first was some printer company. You wouldn't know them."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I waited for the second shot to co..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I waited for the second shot to come -- for me. I thought there would be one. It never came."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Not as much as usual. He'd done a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Not as much as usual. He'd done a line. Plus other things. I was drinking."

fields.Title: You: "(Better not to mention it.) "Then w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Better not to mention it.) "Then what happened?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Yes, but... How did you know that?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, but... How did you know that?"

fields.Title: You: ""You've lied to me about this bulle..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You've lied to me about this bullet before. When I said he was *shot*? You said you're *confused*."

fields.Title: Drama: "She might have been a tad disingenu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She might have been a tad disingenuous when she avoided talking about the bullet in his head *before...*

fields.Title: You: ""But maybe it did?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "But maybe it did?"

fields.Title: You: "When I said the deceased *enjoyed*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: When I said the deceased *enjoyed* his moment of death, she knew it was true. But she said nothing.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant nods in your directi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant nods in your direction: "It checks out."

fields.Title: You: "(Nod.) "Okay.""
fields.Dialogue Text: (Nod.) "Okay."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Thank you." She sounds grateful."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thank you." She sounds grateful.

fields.Title: You: "What's happening?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What's happening?

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""That's cool..." She looks at the a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That's cool..." She looks at the ashtray. Then up at you.

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "Ready for the damage. She knows you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Ready for the damage. She knows you're grilling her.

fields.Title: Volition: "This bastion of willpower here -- h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This bastion of willpower here -- his watchmen have been sleeping too, you can be absolutely certain now. But he's coming around.

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "A little whimper. The young woman h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A little whimper. The young woman hears you. She's looking around.

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "Yes. Start at the top, choose at th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yes. Start at the top, choose at the bottom, it's how we've always done it. No rush...

fields.Title: You: ""Failure to aid a police officer. Y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Failure to aid a police officer. You have wasted our time -- in a time-critical investigation."

fields.Title: Endurance: "Fragile, unshielded, her voice is t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Fragile, unshielded, her voice is thin and tired.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm fixating on it, Kim.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm fixating on it, Kim."

fields.Title: You: ""When Ruby said there would be 'shi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "When Ruby said there would be 'shit' happening if you didn't end your relationship with the deceased -- was she threatening you?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""This is just an assumption.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "This is just an assumption."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Okay. Well..." Her round light bro..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay. Well..." Her round light brown eyes shine with the tears.

fields.Title: You: ""When it happened -- did you hear a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "When it happened -- did you hear a gunshot?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""You've been trying to kick that do..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You've been trying to kick that door down, right?" She points to the barred door, next to the window. "Maybe it leads downstairs?"

fields.Title: Savoir Faire: "She's stuck here. She's already in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She's stuck here. She's already in prison -- look around! She's only trying to help you...

fields.Title: You: ""Why *did* you waste my time then?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why *did* you waste my time then?"

fields.Title: You: ""What happens if they find you?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What happens if they find you?"

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""No. I want to. Let's get this done.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No. I want to. Let's get this done."

fields.Title: You: ""What did you do while they were ha..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What did you do while they were hanging him?"

fields.Title: Volition: "You're not done. She *lied* to you...."
fields.Dialogue Text: You're not done. She *lied* to you. And she's a flight risk -- wake up, man.
